Class All

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soa.policy.wspolicy.PolicyOperator

  • public class All
extends PolicyOperator
    All is an implementation of the WS-Policy All policy operator. An all contains both assertions and other policy operators, all of which are mandatory.
